Package: windcut
Title: Weather Time Series Feature Engineering for Plant Disease Epidemiology
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kaique S.",
           family = "Alves",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kaiquedsalves@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9187-0252"))
Description: Tools for transforming weather time series into model-ready
    features for plant disease epidemiology. The package supports
    relative-time window panes around biological reference dates,
    biologically interpretable weather summaries, feature screening, and
    functional data analysis workflows for comparing weather trajectories
    between disease classes.
